;Shift + Windows + Up (maximize a window across all displays) https://stackoverflow.com/a/9830200/470749
+#Up::
    WinGetActiveTitle, Title
    WinRestore, %Title%
    SysGet, X1, 76
    SysGet, Y1, 77
    SysGet, Width, 78
    SysGet, Height, 79
    WinMove, %Title%,, X1-5, Y1-3, Width +20, Height 
return

